data.description: Step into this charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom home with over 1500 sq. ft. of living space, situated on almost a quarter-acre near the picturesque New Smyrna Beach and Daytona Beach. As you enter, discover a spacious living room and a thoughtfully designed split-bedroom plan, with the master room secluded on one side for added privacy. Enjoy a lovely screened-in back porch and ample backyard. Conveniently located near I-95 and US-1.
